== 播映 ==
《所有的灵魂》起初占据[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]周二晚九点档<ref name="Source2" />，直接在[[真人实境节目|真人实境节目]]《爱的枷锁》后播出<ref name="Source11" /><ref name="Source13" />。电视剧的家长指引评级为{{lang|en|[[美国电视分级制度|TV-PG]]}}，意为“不适合幼儿”<ref name="Source7" />。试播集于2001年4月17日播出<ref name="Books22" />，共有210万观众收看，[[尼尔森媒体研究|尼尔森媒体研究]]结果排在这周所有电视节目的第105位<ref name="Source4" />。

因收视成绩不理想，联合派拉蒙电视网于2001年4月30日暂时停播《所有的灵魂》，此时节目还只播出两集。虽然电视台高管表示尚未决定取消本剧，但媒体评论认为节目反响不佳，取消已成定局<ref name="Source4" /><ref name="Source8">{{cite news | url = http://legacy.sandiegouniontribune.com/tvradio/broadbriefs5.2.html | title = Broadcast Briefs | last = Turegano | first = Preston | date = 2001-05-02 | newspaper = The San Diego Union-Tribune |publisher = Tronc | archivedate = 2018-07-01 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2018-07-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180701193820/http://legacy.sandiegouniontribune.com/tvradio/broadbriefs5.2.html}}</ref>。《所有的灵魂》于八月回归并改占北美东部时区周五晚九点档<ref name="Books22" />，余下的分集都在这个月播完<ref name=":0">{{cite news | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-18947649.html | title = Haunting 'All Souls' returns from great beyond: ; UPN airing pilot, unseen remaining episodes | last = McDonough | first = Kevin | date = 2001-08-03 | newspaper = Charleston Daily Mail | publisher = The Daily Gazette Company | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181119101134/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-18947649.html | archivedate = 2018-11-19 | accessdate = 2018-11-19}}{{subscription required}}</ref>，最后一集在31日播映<ref name="SourceSomething1">{{cite web | url = http://www.tvtango.com/listings/2001/08/31 | title = August 31, 2001 | date = 2001-08-31 | publisher = TV Tango | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180701165232/http://www.tvtango.com/listings/2001/08/31 | archivedate = 2018-07-01}}</ref>。另外还有一集在九月[[重播|重播]]<ref name="SourceSomething2">{{cite web | url = http://www.tvtango.com/listings/2001/09/07 | title = September 7, 2001 | date = 2001-09-07 | publisher = TV Tango | accessdate = 2020-09-05 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905125756/http://www.tvtango.com/listings/2001/09/07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。全剧共计播出360分钟<ref name="Source5">{{cite news | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2015/10/23/the-1657-tv-shows-that-spent-less-time-on-the-air-than-the-hillary-clinton-benghazi-hearing/ | title = The 1,657 TV shows that spent less time on the air than the Hillary Clinton Benghazi hearing | last = Bump | first = Philip | date = 2015-10-23 | newspaper = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | publisher = WP Company LLC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213125828/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2015/10/23/the-1657-tv-shows-that-spent-less-time-on-the-air-than-the-hillary-clinton-benghazi-hearing/ | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

麦考奇（{{lang|en|Grayson McCouch}}）在节目取消后表示，本剧从一开始就“注定要失败”，联合派拉蒙电视网“当时是失败者的电视台”，电视剧也没有得到足够重视。科斯格罗夫（{{lang|en|Daniel Cosgrove}}）不认可麦考奇颇显情绪化的观点，在他看来，节目的失败与电视台没有必然联系。<ref name="Source12">{{cite web | title = ATWT's Grayson McCouch & GL's Daniel Cosgrove | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170930084415/http://www.soapoperadigest.com/content/atwts-grayson-mccouch-gls-daniel-cosgrove-page-2-0/ | date = 2003-08-08 | work = Soap Opera Digest | publisher = American Media, Inc. | url = https://www.soapoperadigest.com/content/atwts-grayson-mccouch-gls-daniel-cosgrove-page-2-0/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2017-09-30 | accessdate = 2020-09-05}}</ref>罗德里格兹觉得《所有的灵魂》“略有些超前”，导致收视成绩差，如果推迟一到两年播映相信效果会好得多<ref name="Books3" />。本剧此后一直没有发行[[数码多功能影音光盘|数码多功能影音光盘]]和[[蓝光光盘|蓝光光盘]]，也没有授权[[流媒体|流媒体]]发布<ref name="SourceHomeRelease">{{cite web | url = http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/shows/Souls/5319 | title = All Souls (2001) | publisher = TVShowsOnDVD.com | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170930131318/http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/shows/Souls/5319 | archivedate = 2017-09-30 | accessdate = 2017-09-30}}</ref>。

== 专业评价 ==
《所有的灵魂》获评论界好评<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source7" /><ref name="Source13" /><ref name=":0" />，《[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]]》的埃里克·明克（{{lang|en|Eric Mink}}）称赞剧中恐怖元素，还称节目能让电视台的核心观众紧张不已，整个人都吓得缩成一团<ref name="Source1" />。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》刊登[[霍华德·罗森伯格|霍华德·罗森伯格]]（{{lang|en|Howard Rosenberg}}）的评论文章，赞赏节目给观众带来“超自然的乐趣”<ref name="Source7" />。凯文·麦克唐纳（{{lang|en|Kevin McDonough}}）在{{lang|en|Lawrence.com}}网站发文，主要表扬节目的剪辑和特效，觉得本剧是“经典的艾伦·斯班林制作”<ref name="Source13" />，他还在《[[查尔斯顿每日邮报|查尔斯顿每日邮报]]》（''{{lang|en|The Charleston Daily Mail}}''）声称《所有的灵魂》是“你从未看过的最好节目”，对电视剧构想和演员青眼有加<ref name=":0" />。明克也认为节目剧情和人物表现出色，有进一步发展潜力<ref name="Source1" />。

部分评论对剧情评价不一<ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source11" /><ref name="Source15" />，[[罗伯·欧文|罗伯·欧文]]（{{lang|en|Rob Owen}}）在《[[匹兹堡邮报|匹兹堡邮报]]》发文，称赞试播集展现的元素足以证明节目潜力<ref name="Source11" />。奥克斯曼认为试播集的恐怖手段行之有效，形体完好胎儿移动的镜头特别出彩<ref name="Source2" />。《[[洛杉矶周报|洛杉矶周报]]》（''{{lang|en|LA Weekly}}''）的罗伯特·劳埃德（{{lang|en|Robert Lloyd}}）一方面觉得电视剧制作精良，雄心尽显，另一方面感觉格雷斯和圣克莱尔初遇时的情节暴露太多剧情<ref name="Source15">{{cite news | url = http://www.laweekly.com/content/printView/2133277 | title = Back to Barbary Lane | last = Lloyd | first = Robert | date = 2001-05-02 | newspaper = LA Weekly | publisher = Voice Media Group | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170930085355/http://www.laweekly.com/content/printView/2133277 | archivedate = 2017-09-30 | accessdate = 2017-09-30}}</ref>。

部分评论将本剧与其他恐怖或科幻电视剧对比<ref name="Source3" /><ref name="Source2" />。古德曼认为《所有的灵魂》与《{{lang|en|X}}档案》、《[[迷離境界|迷離境界]]》、史蒂芬·金1977年的小说《[[闪灵_(小说)|闪灵]]》及其他医疗剧都有相似之处。虽然各种元素在剧中显得“漫无目的”，但整体而言还是达到相互配合的效果。<ref name="Source3" />奥克斯曼批评节目以精神病院为背景的设定不够原创，与金的作品及1996年电影《[[非常手段|非常手段]]》（''{{lang|en|Extreme Measures}}''）类似，如果与《[[雙峰_(1990年電視劇)|双峰]]》相比又显得肤浅。不过，他认为《所有的灵魂》有望成为《{{lang|en|X}}档案》过后[[电视联播网|电视联播网]]上最吓人的节目。<ref name="Source2" />

